item.title: Cycling through the pain
item.author: James Dixon,
item.description: Friday, 18.00. Set off from College in the minibuses. Painstakingly prepared genre-based mix tape 1 out of 6 ‘Reggae’ wobbling out from Transit subwoofer to minimal enthusiasm from backseat passengers – requests for Kraftwerk’s ‘Tour de France’ soundtrack pouring in thick and fast from Sioni. …
